span></span></code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"line-numbers\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"counter-reset:line-number 0\"><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div></div></div><p>。</p>\n<p>总结：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>推荐使用字面量方式声明对象，而不是 <code v-pre>Object</code> 构造函数</li>\n<li><code v-pre>Object.assign</code> 静态方法创建新的对象</li>\n<li><code v-pre>Object.keys</code> 静态方法获取对象中所有属性</li>\n<li><code v-pre>Object.values</code> 表态方法获取对象中所有属性值</li>\n</ol>\n<h5 id=\"array\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#array\"><span>Array</span></a></h5>\n<p><code v-pre>Array</code> 是内置的构造函数，用于创建数组。</p>\n<div class=\"language-html line-numbers-mode\" data-ext=\"html\" data-title=\"html\"><button class=\"copy\" title=\"复制代码\" data-copied=\"已复制\"></button><pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark vp-code\" v-pre=\"\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">&#x3C;</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">script</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\">  // 构造函数创建数组</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">  let</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark